Package: dbkit
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for SQL Server Connections and Data Upserts/Inserts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Guy", "Schvitz",
      email = "guy.schvitz@ec.europa.eu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides helper functions for connecting to Microsoft SQL Server 
    and performing basic data operations. Includes functions for chunked 
    inserts with transaction support and memory-efficient upserts using SQL 
    Server 'MERGE'.
